name: Teen Mom: Young + Pregnant
overview: Ashley, Brianna, Jade, Kayla and Lexi are five teenagers who must navigate the complexities of pregnancy and becoming young mothers.

episodes.name: Eyes on Me
episodes.overview: In the series premiere, Stephan has been cheating on Kayla again. Lexi and her pregnant belly must face the crowd at the first football game of the season. Jade learns drugs are the reason her father was fired. Ashley and Bar get into a fight. Brianna and Danae have plans.

episodes.name: Baby Shower Blowup
episodes.overview: Ashley and Bar's baby shower goes from zero to one hundred, Brianna is caught in the middle of her mom and Danae, Kayla grows concerned that she may end up a single mom.

episodes.name: It's a Baby, Not a Toy
episodes.overview: After the baby shower, Ashley and Bar have a lot to process. Kayla isn't sure what to think about Stephan. Tensions grow between Brianna and Danae while they get ready for Braeson's arrival.

episodes.name: Cutting the Cord
episodes.overview: Lexi’s parents are growing concerned that she and Kyler don’t have a plan for the baby’s arrival; Brianna and Danae escape tensions at home with a trip to Chicago and Jade’s water breaks!

episodes.name: Parenting 101
episodes.overview: Jade struggles to care for Kloie by herself; Ashley and Bar take their last trip with friends before becoming parents; Brianna and Danae get ready to welcome baby Braeson into the world.

episodes.name: Co-Parent Trap
episodes.overview: Brianna and Danae continue to fight while Ashley and Lexi prepare for labor. Jade is the boss, and everyone needs to fall in line or get out!

episodes.name: Tying the...Not
episodes.overview: Brianna and Danae’s relationship is strained by their living arrangements. Jade and Ashley may soon go from Ms. To Mrs.

episodes.name: Leaving the Nest
episodes.overview: Brianna and Danae need a place to stay, while Ashley also grapples with her living situation. Jade’s parents are starting to wear out their welcome.

episodes.name: Louder Than Words
episodes.overview: Brianna & Danae move in with Danae’s mom. Jade’s family plans a dinner. Lexi decides get herself out of the friend zone with Kyler. Kayla helps Stephan when he needs a place to stay. Ashley tries to mend her relationship with her mom.

episodes.name: When Right Feels Wrong
episodes.overview: Lexi takes steps to move on from Kyler. Kayla is caught in the middle of tension between her mom and Stephan. Ashley and Bar move into a new place. Jade questions if she and Sean are meant to be. Brianna makes a big choice about her relationship.

episodes.name: Pomp and Circumstance
episodes.overview: Lexi graduates from high school, Brianna tries to get closure with Danae, Ashley and Bar visit Bar's mom in Las Vegas, and Kayla consults with a lawyer about custody.

episodes.name: Out with the Old, In with the New
episodes.overview: Kayla begins college and reconnects with an old high school friend, Brianna explores her newfound post-breakup independence, and Jade and Sean try counseling.

episodes.name: Moving Too Fast
episodes.overview: Brianna defends her new boyfriend to her sister, Bar makes peace with Ashley's family, Kayla and Stephan come together for Izaiah's medical treatment, and Sean bails on Jade.

episodes.name: For Now
episodes.overview: Lexi and Kyler go on spring break, Brianna asks Robert to move to Oregon, Ashley gets into a brawl with Bar's mom, and Kayla tries to fix Stephan's relationship with her mom.

episodes.name: Live Fast, Dye Young
episodes.overview: Brianna prepares to move to Oregon with her new boyfriend Robert, Kayla urges Stephan to mend fences with her mom, and Lexi puts her foot down and stands up to Kyler.

episodes.name: Stay in Your Lane
episodes.overview: Tensions arise when Ashley gets a restraining order against Bar’s mom, Lexi struggles to prove her independence, and Jade does her best to cut Sean out of her life.

episodes.name: Decisions, Decisions
episodes.overview: Ashley puts Bar's feelings first; Lexi faces a difficult choice; Kayla and Stephan go to court; Jade's anxiety reaches an all-time high; Brianna says hello to Oregon and goodbye to her sister.

episodes.name: Dreams & Nightmares
episodes.overview: Ashley and Bar's trip to Atlanta has surprising consequences; Lexi takes a big step toward pursuing her dream job; Brianna regrets the family move to Oregon; Kayla's relationship with Stephan takes an unexpected turn.

episodes.name: The High Road
episodes.overview: Ashley invites Bar's mom over to make peace; Kyler gives Lexi an ultimatum; Kayla faces a choice that could affect her and Izaiah's lives for years; Jade turns to Sean when Kloie gets sick; Brianna clashes with her mom.

episodes.name: Our Past Is Our Past
episodes.overview: Ashley’s peace with Bar’s mom is short lived. Lexi feels caught between her parents and her boyfriend. Kayla wrestles with a tough decision while Stephan sees his mom for the first time in two years.

episodes.name: Battling Demons
episodes.overview: Brianna focuses on Braeson's first birthday instead of her issues with Robert; Lexi's parents confront her about their problems with Kyler; Ashley and Bar decide to take a break from each other after a bad fight

episodes.name: No Winners
episodes.overview: Ashley is staying at her mom's house after a fight with Bar turned physical and she had to get the police involved; Jade makes Sean take a drug test; Lexi has to let Kyler know that her parents do not want him over at the house.

episodes.name: Now What?
episodes.overview: Ashley is unsure how to move forward after Bar's apology; Jade is frustrated when Sean's attempt to start rehab doesn't go as planned; Lexi's family plans a camping trip and Kyler isn't invited; Brianna struggles with Robert.

episodes.name: One Day You'll Thank Me
episodes.overview: Ashley moves back in with her mom; Jade is relieved when Sean finally starts the drug treatment program; Lexi gets a peek at what her life might have been like when she visits a friend at college; Brianna comes to a realization.

episodes.name: Babies Have It Made
episodes.overview: Ashley asks Bar to stay away from Holly's first birthday party; Jade gets bad news; when Kyler has to pick up the baby from Lexi's mom, Lexi worries about how the two will get along; Brianna wants to go to college.

episodes.name: What Comes Next
episodes.overview: Ashley disappoints her mom and sister. Jade reevaluates her life after her grandmother’s cancer scare. Kyler doesn’t invite his mom to Tobias’s first birthday party. Brianna tries to heal old wounds. Kayla navigates Izaiah’s first birthday.

episodes.name: Three Plus Two
episodes.overview: Ashley gets back on track with school; Kayla realizes she may have to drop out of school to take care of Izaiah; Brianna struggles to balance multiple jobs and childcare; Kiaya is under pressure to make peace with her baby's father.

episodes.name: Mutual Place
episodes.overview: Rachel reaches her breaking point with Drew, Brianna searches for closure with Danae, and Ashley prepares for Bar to reunite with her family at Holly's christening.

episodes.name: No Going Back
episodes.overview: Luke considers his next moves as Kayla's pregnancy news sinks in, Kiaya is upset with Teazha for disrespecting their relationship, and Brianna contacts her estranged father.

episodes.name: Real Recognize Real
episodes.overview: Kayla breaks the news of her pregnancy to her mom, Rachel gives birth to a baby girl, Ashley and Bar work on their relationship, and Brianna gets a paternity test for Braeson.

episodes.name: Ball Is in Your Court
episodes.overview: Brianna gets the results of Braeson's paternity test; Ashley reaches her breaking point with Bar; Kayla tries to give Stephan another chance to be in Izaiah's life; Kiaya starts talking to X'Zayveon again.

episodes.name: That Perfect Family
episodes.overview: Kiaya's water breaks in the middle of the night; Ashley leans into being single; Brianna gets a response from Braeson's father; Kayla realizes she's in a lose-lose situation; Rachel is trying to break the cycle.

episodes.name: Unconvenient
episodes.overview: Ashley tries to have a carefree weekend in Vegas; Brianna consults a lawyer; Rachel resents being compared to Malorie; Kiaya struggles to keep her cool with X'Zayveon's mom.

episodes.name: Beyond Calm
episodes.overview: Kayla and Luke have a gender reveal; Stephan takes his girlfriend to Florida; Ashley and Bar are not on the same page about their status; Rachel's birthday doesn't go exactly as she plans; Brianna goes to the emergency room.

episodes.name: I Deserve My Happiness
episodes.overview: Rachel deals with consequences of not knowing who Hazelee's biological father is. Kiaya visits X'Zayveon in prison for the first time. Ashley goes to LA and Bar overreacts. Brianna's patience is tested.

episodes.name: Don't Feel Bad for Me
episodes.overview: Brianna's frustration with Braeson's father grows, Kayla reaches her breaking point, Rachel misses Jacob, Kiaya and Teazha fight over the past, and Bar shocks Ashley.

episodes.name: History Repeats Itself
episodes.overview: Kayla changes Izaiah's last name; Ashley meets up with a friend she's been talking to on social media; Rachel considers birth control; Kiaya agrees to mediation with X'Zayveon's mom; Brianna flirts with the idea of dating again.

episodes.name: Too Low to Let Go
episodes.overview: Kiaya takes a big step, Brianna and Braeson experience a milestone, Ashley's family faces a major loss, Kayla agrees to talk to Stephan, and Rachel reaches her breaking point.

episodes.name: Can't Back Out Now
episodes.overview: Brianna considers signing up for a dental assistant program, Kiaya pushes Teazha to connect with X'Zayveon after his release from prison, and Kayla prepares to move to Iowa.

episodes.name: Looking for Signs
episodes.overview: Brianna spends time with her new friend Jayden, Ashley graduates from her medical assistant program, and Kayla has mixed feelings about her mom's decision to move to Iowa.

episodes.name: Not Gonna Be Like That Again
episodes.overview: Kayla's mom finds an apartment in the same building Kayla and Luke are moving into, Brianna and her new man Jayden take a step forward, and Kiaya and Teazha go to counseling.

episodes.name: Out of My Comfort Zone
episodes.overview: Rachel makes a hard decision, Brianna can't please everyone at Braeson's birthday party, Kiaya's date with Teazha backfires, and Kayla welcomes her new daughter.

episodes.name: Where Do You Go From Here?
episodes.overview: Kayla grows frustrated with stay-at-home mom life, Ashley takes Holly to L.A. when Bar bails on watching her, and Brianna gives Jayden an ultimatum about talking to his ex.

episodes.name: Putting Myself First
episodes.overview: Brianna reconnects with an ex, Kiaya struggles with her breakup, Rachel receives heartbreaking news, Bar pushes Ashley too far, and Kayla and Luke celebrate Izaiah's birthday.

episodes.name: Long Time No See
episodes.overview: Kayla questions Stephan's renewed interest in Izaiah, Brianna's new friendship creates a rift between her and her mom, and Kiaya tries to define her relationship with Teazha.

episodes.name: High Noon
episodes.overview: Rachel considers moving in with her sister Malorie, Madisen deals with her and Christian's breakup, and both Kiaya and Kayla struggle to keep the peace with their kids' paternal grandmas.

episodes.name: Grandmama Drama
episodes.overview: Kayla has a tense meeting with Stephan's mother, Rachel gets in touch with her ex, Kiaya works on mending personal relationships and Brianna experiences more friction with her mother.

episodes.name: Family Ties
episodes.overview: New cast member Kayla J asks her ex Makel about getting back together, Brianna hopes therapy will help her work things out with her mom, and Kayla talks with Luke about stability for Izaiah.

episodes.name: All About Adjustments
episodes.overview: Kiaya plans a surprise birthday for Teazha, Brianna takes the lead on Braeson's potty training, and Rachel rents an Airbnb to get some space from her mom.

episodes.name: Turning Point
episodes.overview: Kayla gets a surprising message from her ex-boyfriend, Kayla J and Makel attempt to keep the peace as they prepare Mecca for her first day of school, and Rachel begrudgingly returns home.Less

episodes.name: Do Better
episodes.overview: Rachel makes plans to leave home, Kayla meets up with her ex, Brianna dips her toe back in the dating pool, Kayla J opens up about her childhood in therapy, and Kiaya reaches out to Carla.

episodes.name: Back to Reality
episodes.overview: Brianna's new relationship puts a strain on her friendship with Ashley, Rachel feels the pinch of her newfound independence, and Kiaya tries to make sense of her relationship with Teazha.

episodes.name: New Dude, New Mood
episodes.overview: Kiaya and Teazha try to mend things after a fight, Kayla considers going into therapy with Luke, Rachel learns she may have to move in with her mom, and Brianna re-enters the dating scene.

episodes.name: Come Correct
episodes.overview: Kayla J rules out changing Mecca's routine to accommodate Makel, Kayla and Luke revisit old emotional wounds in therapy, and Rachel wants Drew to prove he's worthy of being Hazelee's dad.

episodes.name: Emergency Contact
episodes.overview: Kayla clashes with Luke's family, Makel confronts his unsupportive mom, Rachel awaits Drew's release from prison, and Kiaya and Brianna reach breaking points in their relationships.

episodes.name: Two Steps Forward, One Step Back
episodes.overview: Rachel's long-term plans with Noah hits a snag, Brianna feels unsupported in her decision to move out, Kayla J meets with Makel and his girlfriend, and Kayla makes a heartbreaking decision.

episodes.name: California Love
episodes.overview: Kayla lets the other moms in on a personal struggle, Dr. Drew questions Brianna about her relationship with her mother, and Madisen and Christian give their romance another try.

episodes.name: Family Matters
episodes.overview: An altercation between Kiaya & Teazha’s family forces Teazha to question who her true family is. Kayla & Luke continue to navigate drama. The future is unclear for Madisen & Christian, but a sudden change in living arrangements forces them to make peace.

episodes.name: We Are The Adults
episodes.overview: Kiaya connects with Amour’s dad in prison and realizes that they may not be on the same page when it comes to co-parenting. Luke & Kayla want to end the drama with Luke’s family. Brianna confronts her mom about spending too much time with Braeson.

episodes.name: He Love Me!
episodes.overview: Kayla wants to make peace with Luke's family but hits some roadblocks, Rachel's past comes back to bite her, and Brianna dips her toes back into the dating pool.

episodes.name: They Were Together
episodes.overview: Luke struggles after the blowup between Kayla and his family, Madisen and Christian take a big step in rekindling their bond, and tensions from Kiaya's past loom over Amour's birthday.

episodes.name: Out of the Blue
episodes.overview: Madisen is offended by her dad’s blunt life advice, Brianna faces the end of a friendship, Kiaya receives bad news about X'Zayveon, and Rachel questions whether Hazelee’s dad can change.

episodes.name: The Next Step
episodes.overview: Rachel faces a challenging Valentine's Day, Kayla opens up about some difficult hurdles with her therapist, and Kiaya reaches out to X'Zayveon's mom in hopes of making coparenting work.

episodes.name: Relationship Woes
episodes.overview: Financial stress pushed Madisen and Christian to a breaking point, Brianna tries dating again, Kiaya encourages Teazha to reconnect with family, and Kayla has doubts about her engagement.

episodes.name: Happy Birthday Hazelee!
episodes.overview: Madisen visits Rachel to celebrate Hazelee's third birthday, while Brianna worries about sending Braeson to a school that censors the LGBTQ+ community and Black Lives Matter moment.

episodes.name: Girls Just Wanna Have Fun
episodes.overview: The moms take a group trip to sunny Los Angeles for a promotional photoshoot, where they celebrate Rachel's 20th birthday, de-stress with beach yoga and bond over coparenting struggles.
